    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/0c82bc632c179c3105eeb6c58dad9588.poster.avif?t=1755090572\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/0c82bc632c179c3105eeb6c58dad9588.webm?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/0c82bc632c179c3105eeb6c58dad9588.mp4?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/d13ec46945e78938ff03bd5e08c39a08.avif?t=1755090572\" width=617 height=78 /></span><br><br>独自或与朋友携手，体验《尘封大陆》的终极版本——沙之王国 (Reign of Sand)。驾驭永恒之地的狂沙，在震撼人心的动作角色扮演战斗中，凭借毁天灭地的力量击败传奇怪物。<br> <br>掌握沙的力量，召唤毁灭性的武器，收集敌人的精华，定制属于你自己的战斗风格。在单人或与朋友合作的叙事战役中，为人类开启一个新时代。打破枷锁，释放风暴！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/faea26e86454052bbf641f555478b3ba.webp?t=1755090572\" width=615 height=55 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/469b7d4a320863d378938b4712453912.poster.avif?t=1755090572\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/469b7d4a320863d378938b4712453912.webm?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/469b7d4a320863d378938b4712453912.mp4?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>更大的世界、全新的敌人、重制的升级系统、全新的任务……《尘封大陆》的世界将因此次免费重大更新而更加丰富多彩！享受全新的配音，体验重制的战役，对抗拥有全新精华石的更加强大的生物。在万众期盼的“新游戏+”模式中接续你的冒险，挑战梦魇难度下的诸神。在此次内容丰富的全新版本中，还有更多惊喜和改进等你探索！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/78871211401c8e69bcc2e81c40e5363c.webp?t=1755090572\" width=615 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/e651735db31ace30b8626e1665ddcb68.poster.avif?t=1755090572\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/e651735db31ace30b8626e1665ddcb68.webm?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/e651735db31ace30b8626e1665ddcb68.mp4?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>在这片荒凉世界的沙丘上疾驰游历，揭开这个世界的奥秘，解放深受压迫的民众。得益于重制的升级系统和重新配音的叙事战役，现在正是开始你的冒险的最佳时机。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/0f09161513831aae48aec5d71426f142.webp?t=1755090572\" width=615 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/f44bd3ce95beaf8b1bd27d0bb1fa10a6.poster.avif?t=1755090572\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/f44bd3ce95beaf8b1bd27d0bb1fa10a6.webm?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/f44bd3ce95beaf8b1bd27d0bb1fa10a6.mp4?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>在“新游戏+”模式中新增的梦魇难度下，两人携手并不足以对抗诸神。接受瑟洛斯的新挑战，直面拥有独特能力而又前所未见的传奇怪物。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/41999adf9610b0761ee947ab43208856.webp?t=1755090572\" width=615 height=49 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/2a94a746c9b63d8e84faa5cdb5806c4f.poster.avif?t=1755090572\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/2a94a746c9b63d8e84faa5cdb5806c4f.webm?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230530/extras/2a94a746c9b63d8e84faa5cdb5806c4f.mp4?t=1755090572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>释放你的拳铠之力，用流畅、动态且完全可定制的战斗系统铸造属于你的传奇。沙之王国 (Reign of Sand)还将加入更多精华石和独特护甲，以前所未有的能力强化你的武器库。",
